Families
========
O: kanjiVariant '-04' is supported.
P: We have '-04' maps, but fonts lack some glyphs
X: We don't have '-04' maps.

O noEmbed
    (no font needed for dvipdfmx)

X ms
    msmincho.ttc
    msgothic.ttc
X ipa
    ipam.ttf
    ipag.ttf
X ipaex
    ipaexm.ttf
    ipaexg.ttf

O? hiragino-pro
    HiraMinPro-W2.otf
    HiraMinPro-W3.otf
    HiraMinPro-W6.otf
    HiraKakuPro-W3.otf
    HiraKakuPro-W6.otf
    HiraKakuStd-W8.otf
    HiraMaruPro-W4.otf

